00:37:49.860 --> 00:37:53.340
principle with respect to
another metalloprotein,

00:37:53.340 --> 00:37:54.300
which is hemoglobin.

00:37:54.300 --> 00:37:58.350
So hemoglobin has a "heme,"
which is iron, more d-orbitals.

00:37:58.350 --> 00:38:01.110
