00:38:08.820 --> 00:38:13.570
So hemoglobin Hb plus
oxygen yields oxyhemoglobin.

00:38:13.570 --> 00:38:15.610
It's hemoglobin
with oxygen bound.

00:38:15.610 --> 00:38:17.520
And this is an incredibly
important reaction,

00:38:17.520 --> 00:38:20.960
because otherwise your air,
your O2, would be in your lungs

00:38:20.960 --> 00:38:22.050
and wouldn't leave.

00:38:22.050 --> 00:38:24.020
But hemoglobin carries
